title: LF Team plat-diamond Supp main
body:
Used to be d3-d4 peaked d1 but stopped playing and decayed and now i am getting back into league. LF team to play with and get good again.
http://www.lolking.net/summoner/oce/354816#profile (link to see the decay) currently p4  :(

replies.body: Have a team comprised of mid gold to plats if you are interested we could definitely use you we use discord for games if interested let me know.
